description: UFC on ESPN: Cannonier vs. Gastelum (also known as UFC on ESPN 29) is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that will take place on August 21, 2021, at the UFC Apex facility in Enterprise, Nevada, part of the Las Vegas Metropolitan Area, United States.
